145
00:09:21,200 --> 00:09:24,352
and these bastards, they steal
your synthesizers and er...

146
00:09:24,400 --> 00:09:26,960
- Yes, it's a shame.
- Yes, it is a shame.

147
00:09:27,000 --> 00:09:28,639
Now, Synthesizer Patel,

148
00:09:28,680 --> 00:09:31,832
synthesizers come in all sorts
of shapes and sizes.

149
00:09:31,880 --> 00:09:34,679
This one here, for instance,
looks like a calculator.

150
00:09:34,720 --> 00:09:36,871
Ah. That is quite right, Pealy.

151
00:09:36,920 --> 00:09:40,072
That is because it is
a calculating synthesizer.

