00:09:40,120 --> 00:09:43,670
It is similar to the one used by
the Chancellor of the Exchequer

153
00:09:43,720 --> 00:09:45,473
in his recent musical budget.

154
00:09:46,400 --> 00:09:49,552
So it's ideal for anyone
who loves music and maths?

155
00:09:49,600 --> 00:09:53,480
Exactly and there is security lock
here for extra security,

156
00:09:53,520 --> 00:09:56,399
because synthesizers
are so expensive and...

157
00:09:56,440 --> 00:10:00,559
Now, Synthesizer Patel, I've never
seen an instrument like this before.

158
00:10:00,600 --> 00:10:04,037
- That looks like water.
- It is indeed water, Pealy.

159
00:10:04,080 --> 00:10:08,279
The water makes it easier for the
hands to move around over the keys.

160
00:10:08,320 --> 00:10:10,960
It also makes the music sound
smoother.

