the wonderful world of synthesizers.

168
00:10:28,040 --> 00:10:30,953
They really are amazing devices,
aren't they?

169
00:10:31,000 --> 00:10:33,993
Synthesizer Patel, you mentioned
earlier the bassoon.

170
00:10:34,040 --> 00:10:37,192
When do you think a synthesizer
will be able to imitate one?

171
00:10:37,240 --> 00:10:39,197
