172
00:10:39,240 --> 00:10:42,836
The bassoon is such a particular
instrument with such a unique sound,

173
00:10:42,880 --> 00:10:45,031
I don't think they'll ever
approximate it.

174
00:10:45,080 --> 00:10:46,878
Certainly not in my lifetime.

175
00:10:46,920 --> 00:10:50,072
I suppose that's good news
for all you bassoonists out there.

